{"tid":1593805,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊：政府已研究《蒙面法》 是否推行需考慮效果和後果","createTime":"2019-09-25T08:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:20.000Z","uid":272531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72682fe7ae6efde976c010ee8da99b55b4d5f3e3","tid":1593805,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊早前曾稱政府已對《反蒙面法》已進行一定的法律上研究，多名建制派人士亦建議就《反蒙面法》立法。鄭若驊今早出發前往南韓前,被問到《反蒙面法》的立法工作，以及會否擔心立法對現時的社會形勢火上加油時，她重申，政府有就《反蒙面法》作相關法律研究，至於會否推行，要考慮很多因素，例如是否透過《緊急法》去推行、對社會帶來的影響，以及引入相關法律的效果和後果。她說，注意到有人提到先在立法會通過，這要視乎政策局方面會否考慮這一點，如果有議員以私人議案形式提出，律政司會在法律上檢視，但最終仍然要相關政策局和行政長官同意，才能提交立法會。<br />\n<br />\n.............<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60081995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60081995&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9L6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=373aa334\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60081995&h=3cd55496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60081995</a>"},{"pid":"a4cc5116695eae5f9c4bb30fe09d1651080dbd93","tid":1593805,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"Burqa計唔計？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97ed9df62379635b0269b44951cbaa628d1a22c","tid":1593805,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/